trans-unit.source: Represents a view of an instance.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en visning av en forekomst.

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstanceStore.Execute*> method implementations return an InstanceView object that provides a view into the instance data in the persistence store.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel den <xref:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstanceStore.Execute*>metoden implementeringer returnere et InstanceView-objekt som gir en oversikt over forekomstdataene i vedvarende lager.</xref:System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstanceStore.Execute*>

trans-unit.source: Each InstanceView object is associated with an InstanceHandle.
trans-unit.target: Hvert InstanceView-objekt er knyttet til en InstanceHandle.

trans-unit.source: For an InstanceView returned from InstanceStore.Execute, the associated handle is the one passed to Execute.
trans-unit.target: For en InstanceView returnert fra InstanceStore.Execute, er tilknyttede referansen sendt til Execute.

trans-unit.source: For an InstanceView returned from InstancePersistenceContext.InstanceView, the associated handle is the one passed to TryCommand.
trans-unit.target: For en InstanceView returnert fra InstancePersistenceContext.InstanceView, er tilknyttede referansen sendt til TryCommand.

trans-unit.source: An InstanceHandle may have zero or more InstanceView objects associated with it at any given time.
trans-unit.target: En InstanceHandle kan ha null eller flere objekter for InstanceView tilknyttet om gangen.

trans-unit.source: InstanceView objects returned from InstanceStore.Execute are immutable and represent a snapshot of the known instance state after the successful execution of that command.
trans-unit.target: InstanceView objekter ble returnert fra InstanceStore.Execute er uforanderlig og representerer et øyeblikksbilde av tilstanden kjente forekomsten etter vellykket kjøring av kommandoen.

trans-unit.source: InstanceView objects returned from InstancePersistenceContext are mutable and represent the current known instance state as it is being updated during the execution of the command.
trans-unit.target: InstanceView objekter ble returnert fra InstancePersistenceContext er ruletemplatevariable og representerer gjeldende status for kjente forekomsten som den oppdateres under utførelse av kommandoen.

trans-unit.source: (If the command ultimately fails, this intermediate state is discarded).
trans-unit.target: (Hvis kommandoen mislykkes til slutt, forkastes problemet mellomliggende).

trans-unit.source: Gets instance data as a dictionary of names and values.
trans-unit.target: Henter forekomstdataene som en ordliste for navn og verdier.

trans-unit.source: The instance data.
trans-unit.target: Forekomstdataene.

trans-unit.source: Gets the consistency status of the InstanceData property.
trans-unit.target: Henter konsekvens status for egenskapen InstanceData.

trans-unit.source: The consistency (None, In Doubt, and Partial) of the instance data.
trans-unit.target: (Ingen, usikker og delvis) for konsekvent forekomstdataene.

trans-unit.source: InstanceValueConsistency.None indicates that the InstanceData property holds a fully populated and locked set of instance data.
trans-unit.target: InstanceValueConsistency.None indikerer egenskapen InstanceData inneholder et fullstendig fylt og låst sett med forekomstdataene.

trans-unit.source: Gets the identifier (ID) of the instance as a GUID.
trans-unit.target: Henter identifikator (ID) for forekomsten som en GUID.

trans-unit.source: The ID of the instance or Guid.Empty if the associated instance handle is not bound to an instance.
trans-unit.target: IDen for forekomsten eller Guid.Empty Hvis håndtaket tilknyttede forekomsten ikke er bundet til en forekomst.

trans-unit.source: Gets the instance keys as a dictionary of instance key identifiers and associated <xref href="System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstanceKeyView"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Henter nøklene forekomsten som en ordliste for nøkkelen forekomst-IDer og tilknyttede <xref href="System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstanceKeyView"> </xref> objekter.

trans-unit.source: A dictionary of instance key identifiers and their associated instance key view objects.
trans-unit.target: En ordliste for forekomsten key identifikatorer og tilknyttede forekomsten key Vis objekter.

trans-unit.source: Gets the consistency status of the InstanceKeys property.
trans-unit.target: Henter konsekvens status for egenskapen InstanceKeys.

trans-unit.source: The consistency value of instance keys.
trans-unit.target: Konsekvenskontroll verdien for forekomsten nøkler.

trans-unit.source: InstanceValueConsistency.None indicates that the InstanceKeys property holds a fully populated and locked set of instance keys (though not necessarily each key’s metadata).
trans-unit.target: InstanceValueConsistency.None angir egenskapen InstanceKeys inneholder et fullstendig fylt og låst sett med forekomsten nøkler (og ikke nødvendigvis hver nøkkel metadata).

trans-unit.source: Gets the metadata of an instance as a dictionary of names and <xref href="System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstanceValue"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Henter metadata for en forekomst som en ordliste for navn og <xref href="System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstanceValue"> </xref> objekter.

trans-unit.source: The metadata of the instance.
trans-unit.target: Metadata for forekomsten.

trans-unit.source: Gets the consistency status of the InstanceMetadata property.
trans-unit.target: Henter konsekvens status for egenskapen InstanceMetadata.

trans-unit.source: The consistency of the instance metadata.
trans-unit.target: Konsekvenskontroll av metadata for forekomsten.

trans-unit.source: InstanceValueConsistency.None indicates that the InstanceMetadata property holds a fully populated and locked set of instance metadata.
trans-unit.target: InstanceValueConsistency.None angir egenskapen InstanceMetadata inneholder et fullstendig fylt og låst sett med metadata for forekomsten.

trans-unit.source: Gets the owner of the instance.
trans-unit.target: Henter eieren av forekomsten.

trans-unit.source: The owner of the instance.
trans-unit.target: Eieren av forekomsten.

trans-unit.source: Returns null if the associated instance handle is not bound to an instance owner.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer null hvis den tilknyttede forekomstreferansen ikke er bundet til en forekomst eier.

trans-unit.source: Gets the metadata for an instance owner as a dictionary of names and values.
trans-unit.target: Henter metadata for en eier av forekomsten som en ordliste for navn og verdier.

trans-unit.source: A dictionary containing instance-owner metadata.
trans-unit.target: En liste som inneholder forekomsten eieren metadata.

trans-unit.source: Gets the consistency status of the InstanceOwnerMetadata property.
trans-unit.target: Henter konsekvens status for egenskapen InstanceOwnerMetadata.

trans-unit.source: The consistency of the instance owner metadata.
trans-unit.target: Forekomsten eieren metadataene er konsekvent.

trans-unit.source: Returns null if the associated instance handle is not bound to an instance owner.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer null hvis den tilknyttede forekomstreferansen ikke er bundet til en forekomst eier.

trans-unit.source: Gets the state of the instance (Unknown, Uninitialized, Initialized, or Completed).
trans-unit.target: Får statusen for forekomsten (ukjent Uninitialized, initialisert eller fullført).

trans-unit.source: The state of the instance.
trans-unit.target: Statusen for forekomsten.

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of <xref href="System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstanceStoreQueryResult"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Henter en samling av <xref href="System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstanceStoreQueryResult"> </xref> objekter.

trans-unit.source: The collection is automatically reset to empty each time a command is executed against the associated instance handle.
trans-unit.target: Samlingen tilbakestilles automatisk til tom hver gang en kommando kjøres mot tilknyttede forekomsten-referanse.
